00:15:04.080 --> 00:15:08.310
So before we talk about our
strategies and tips for

00:15:08.310 --> 00:15:11.180
backward compatibility, and
specifically for designing for

00:15:11.180 --> 00:15:13.730
backward compatibility, not so
